author: Disney
description:
Go behind the scenes of Disneyland Handcrafted with award-winning director Leslie Iwerks. Disneyland Handcrafted, available on @Disney YouTube and streaming on @disneyplus January 22, 2026.
 
In this exclusive interview, Leslie shares her personal connection to Disney, her family’s legendary legacy, and the creative process behind making this stunning documentary. Discover how rare archival footage was restored, the artistry behind Disneyland’s handmade details, and the stories that bring the park’s craftsmanship to life.
 
🎥 What You’ll Learn in This Video:
· Leslie Iwerks’ Disney lineage and storytelling roots
· How Disneyland Handcrafted celebrates Walt Disney and Disneyland’s artisans and creators
· The process of pulling and restoring historic Disney archives
· Behind-the-scenes insights into documentary filmmaking
